    gnd "De volta ao filme."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieDates/jamiemoviedate.rpy:105
translate portuguese jamiemovietheaterstartdate_43311053:

    # "During the movie, she keeps looking over at me and smiling."
    "Durante o filme, ela não pára de olhar para mim e de sorrir."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieDates/jamiemoviedate.rpy:107
translate portuguese jamiemovietheaterstartdate_610dce56:

    # "She seems to be liking the movie okay."
    "Parece estar a gostar do filme."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieDates/jamiemoviedate.rpy:110
translate portuguese jamiemovietheaterstartdate_ffcd1a92:

    # "She seems to lose interest in the movie fairly quickly."
    "Parece perder o interesse pelo filme bastante depressa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieDates/jamiemoviedate.rpy:111
translate portuguese jamiemovietheaterstartdate_5973f780:

    # "I don't know. It's pretty fun to me. I guess she just doesn't like this kind of movie."
    "Não sei. Para mim é bastante divertido. Acho que ela simplesmente não gosta deste tipo de filme."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieDates/jamiemoviedate.rpy:114
translate portuguese jamiemovietheaterstartdate_4f23a069:

    # "During every scary scene that happens she tenses up and covers her mouth."
    "Durante todas as cenas assustadoras, ela fica tensa e tapa a boca."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieDates/jamiemoviedate.rpy:115
translate portuguese jamiemovietheaterstartdate_603a9a9b:

    # "Sometimes she even puts her hands over her eyes."
    "Às vezes, chega mesmo a tapar os olhos com as mãos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieDates/jamiemoviedate.rpy:116
translate portuguese jamiemovietheaterstartdate_288b2f3c:

    # "Then the music goes quiet, and I know that a jumpscare is coming."
    "Depois, a música fica em silêncio e eu sei que se aproxima um susto repentino."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieDates/jamiemoviedate.rpy:119
translate portuguese jamiemovietheaterstartdate_e86e1727:

    # "She grabs my arm and tucks her head down into it."
    "Ela agarra-me o braço e encosta a cabeça nele."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieDates/jamiemoviedate.rpy:120
translate portuguese jamiemovietheaterstartdate_6bdb4e54:

    # "Her fingers dig into my arm, grasping it so tight."
    "Os dedos dela cravam-se no meu braço, agarrando-o com tanta força."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieDates/jamiemoviedate.rpy:122
translate portuguese jamiemovietheaterstartdate_e7200fcd:

    # "For the rest of the movie, I put my arm around her and hold her while we watch."
    "Durante o resto do filme, coloco o meu braço à volta dela e abraço-a enquanto vemos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieDates/jamiemoviedate.rpy:125
translate portuguese jamiemovietheaterstartdate_ec13a563:

    # "The movie is funny from pretty much the very beginning."
    "O filme é engraçado praticamente desde o início."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieDates/jamiemoviedate.rpy:126
translate portuguese jamiemovietheaterstartdate_4caf9a58:

    # "And we laugh together all the way through it."
